@tox-user IMHO Tox needs a full rebranding. This includes website, logo, making a responsive newsletter, refined user-interfaces, etc. The doc' needs to be polished (design), the wiki should be replaced by the doc, the blog should be integrated to the website. Many small issues that makes Tox feels less appealing that other IM softwares (ie. Wire, Tungsten, Ring, etc).

@nurupo Those are **not** PlayStation buttons, just basic shapes anyone can' make xD. You can't copyright a square, or a triangle, right?

Tox branding is pretty poor as I see it. We have no guidelines, stylesguide, or anything that could help the ''Tox'' brand to be rememberable easily. Tox branding **is** broken. I'm trying to fix that :)
